      "writtenOn": "2020-08-19T18:54:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Responding an error might be better. It prevents using extra computing resource when there is clearly no matched results. It also prompt users that their createBy format is wrong otherwise they may not know why there is no matching results.\n\nBTW, this is also what Py does.",
      "parentUuid": "0bb04997_4eff6e52",
      "revId": "37e59ff37fbae32e99d33966d640b89c9d25491d",
      "serverId": "3ce6091f-6c88-37e8-8c75-72f92ae8dfba",
